Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,泪的咆哮 你是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的是…鸣人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种压迫感是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那红色的查克拉又是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…是怪物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.90,0:02:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才会说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不把你送给大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才会说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算把你的手脚给折断
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火遁.豪火球之术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该清醒点了吧 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是还没清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把你打到动弹不得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后带你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这既没父母也没兄弟的混小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能体会我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小就孤单一人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底能明白些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为有着亲情的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会感到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了他们之后的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又怎么能明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不了解真正的父母兄弟之情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我请客 你就放开吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和伊鲁卡老师在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾想象过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做忍者还是得先填饱肚子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乘机大吃一顿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我有爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否就是这样的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你在一起的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊 你这拖后腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:06:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会输给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你怎么说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别随便碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想兄弟或许就是这种感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会如此对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是好不容易得来的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…一定要阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.80,0:07:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不会再回头的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我来斩断这份羁绊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要斩断这份羁绊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么到现在还戴着护额
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承认 你是很强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你和我一样都了解孤独的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这份痛苦 会让人变得坚强起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.30,0:08:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为如此 我才要斩断这份羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从而得到更为强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始 我要和你平等对决
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无法伤到我额头的一分一毫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点是永远不会改变的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来和你说什么都是白费口舌了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.60,0:08:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闲聊就此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后 你我之间只有战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看清了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才一直无法捕捉的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可以看清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看清了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助的动作和之前完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 决不能输啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为身体渐渐习惯了咒印状态的缘故吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙移动的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身微妙的力道分布
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他的下一个动作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清楚地浮现在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有此眼力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不会白白浪费查克拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为咒印实在太消耗体力了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然能看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我只要掌握先机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对准此刻看到的鸣人之后的动作…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的动作完全被他看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这条路没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有种不祥的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火遁.龙火之术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好强…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都晚了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经晚了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 你真够弱的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大爷我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:15:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再感谢一下把我封印在\N你这种小鬼体内的第四代火影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经看穿了鸣人的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他身上的查克拉却做出了不同的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去查克拉好像有意识自己在动一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我的眼睛也无法看透
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股红色的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非寻常的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标果然是鸣人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带走鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的组织晓所下达的至上命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你小子有着特别的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我总算明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火遁.豪火球之术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那种查克拉保护着他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持距离作战的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就抓不到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 这到底是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能躲开就很不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要赶上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦借用了这股力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后会变成什么样我也不清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这也没办法啊 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比你更特别
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.65,0:22:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 身体好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外 左手几乎毫无感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这股力量并不能一直用下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.65,0:22:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.55,0:22:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.35,0:23:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的一击 就是最后的一击
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.25,0:23:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泪雨的终结